  "title": "Assistant Section Head/Assistant Pastry Chef (Central Production)",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1><p><strong>Baker & Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery & foodstore is hiring!</p><h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3><p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p><p>✅ 5-days work week [Rostered], 8am to 530pm<br /></p><p>🍕 Location: Commonwealth Capital Building (7 Buroh Lane, Singapore 618291)<br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Assist the Section Head (Pastry Chef) and Production manager in daily running of the Pastry production kitchen<a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Assist the Section Head (Pastry Chef) to develop new recipes and keep up with trend</li><li>Leads and motivates junior pastry cook in the preparation of daily pastry products with consistent quality</li><li>Involvement in daily production of pastry products in accordance with specifications from recipes</li><li>Monitor and order ingredients and supplies</li><li>Ensure safe and proper use of equipment at all times</li><li>Maintain a high standard of cleanliness in and around workstation and strictly abide with health/sanitation regulations</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational need</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Certificate in Pastry Skills or its equivalent</li><li>Preferably 1 year managerial or 2 years supervisory experience in large quantity production</li><li>Ability to work independently as well as in a team</li><li>5 working days per week with the ability to work on weekends/public holidays</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Medical + dental benefits</li><li>Birthday vouchers</li><li>Staff discounts across brands</li></ul><p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7<br /></p><p>** T&C applies</p>",
